<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-05-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-05-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="143" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d143">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/4513</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_MIN1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Morris</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stockholm</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-05-09">
                                        <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1917</hi></date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 10.15 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>346. Prime Ministers and Foreign Ministers of Denmark and Norway have
                                arrived in Sweden to-day to confer with Swedish Government regarding
                                matters of mutual interest. I learn this is for similar purpose
                                other conferences held by these three countries heretofore.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_MIN1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morris</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>